Package: aurelius
Type: Package
Version: 0.8.4
Date: 2017-01-13
Title: Generates PFA Documents from R Code and Optionally Runs Them
Description: Converts R syntax into PFA and provides tools for assembling a PFA
    document within R. Tests validity and runtime behavior of PFA by offloading
    PFA and data to Titus (through rPython). Facilitates conversion of common R
    model output to PFA using aurelius.* libraries.
